<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:27:84">
	Due to Inflation and the rising cost of living, resources are more sparse than ever, but the overwhelming demand for housing, rent assistance, and utility assistance persists. The Salvation Army does not close its doors to people experiencing poverty, even in times of&nbsp;financial crisis like the one we are experiencing now. Please consider becoming a Bed &amp; Bread Club member today so we can continue to Do the Most Good for those in need, no matter the circumstances.
</p>
